Here are all 13 SQL queries combined in one message based on your provided student details:

1. Create Database

```sql
CREATE DATABASE StudentDB;
```

1. Delete Database

```sql
DROP DATABASE StudentDB;
```

1. Create Table

```sql
CREATE TABLE Students (
    Id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY,
    Name VARCHAR(100),
    Department VARCHAR(50),
    Mark INT
);
```

1. Delete Table

```sql
DROP TABLE Students;
```

1. Rename Table

```sql
ALTER TABLE Students RENAME TO Learners;
```

