1. Select All Data

```sql
SELECT * FROM Students;
```

1. Select Specific Columns

```sql
SELECT Name, Mark FROM Students;
```

1. Select First N Rows

```sql
SELECT * FROM Students LIMIT 3;
```

1. Select Last N Rows

```sql
SELECT * FROM Students LIMIT 5 OFFSET 3;
```

1. Order by Specific Column


SELECT * FROM Students ORDER BY Mark DESC;


1. Order by Multiple Columns


SELECT * FROM Students ORDER BY Department ASC, Mark DESC;


1. Aggregate Functions

SELECT
  COUNT(Id) AS TotalStudents,
  SUM(Mark) AS TotalMarks,
  AVG(Mark) AS AverageMarks,
  MAX(Mark) AS HighestMark,
  MIN(Mark) AS LowestMark
FROM Students;

SELECT * FROM Students WHERE Mark > 70;
